title: 11/16 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC) & Best Stashes
description:
Can we trust the "stud" RBs Melvin Gordon, LeSean McCoy and Leonard Fournette this week (7:30)? We get into that after we talk about stashing Ezekiel Elliott, Aaron Rodgers and the rest of the best stashes in Fantasy (2:55) ... Some Die Hard team names (15:10) plus Start or Sit questions for Thursday night (20:30) ... NE-OAK (26:00), TB-MIA (35:48), ARI-HOU (44:34), BUF-LAC (50:28), CIN-DEN (56:30), JAC-CLE (1:01:10) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
